canTravel(int, String) - Method in interface ResortControl
Returns true if a PearlCard is allowed to move on the shuttle, false otherwise A move can be made if: the rating of the pearlCard >= the rating of the destination asteroid AND the destination asteroid is not full AND the pearlCard has sufficient credits AND the pearlCard is currently in the source asteroid AND the pearlCard id is for a pearlCard on the system AND the shuttle code is the code for a shuttle on the system
